cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a deep learning architecture for multi-task learning, specifically for text classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of external memory and neural networks also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the experiments involve text classification, which could also place the paper in the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) category.
